#include <stdio.h>
int main()
{
	long long int n1,n2,count = 0,i;
	while(scanf("%lld",&n1) && n1)
	{
		count += 1;
		scanf("%lld",&n2);
		if(n1>n2)
		{
			long long int temp = n1;
			n1 = n2;
			n2 = temp;
		}
		long long int a[10];
		for(i=0;i<10;i++)
			a[i] = 0;
		while(n1<=n2)
		{
			long long int temp = n1;
			while(temp)
			{
				a[temp%10] += 1;
				temp /= 10;
			}
			n1 += 1;
		}
		printf("Case %lld: ",count);
		for(i=0;i<9;i++)
		{
			printf("%lld:%lld ",i,a[i]);
		}
		printf("%lld:%lld\n",i,a[i]);
	}
	return 0;
}
